text: William Meehan Lonsdale (born 16 September 1986) is a New Zealand cricketer. He is a left arm medium fast bowler and a right hand middle order batsman. He made his first class debut against the Wellington Firebirds in 2007. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand cricketers Category:Canterbury cricketers
